<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<%- include("../components/landing/head") %>

<body class="landing-page legal-page">
  <%- include("../components/landing/header") %>

  <main class="legal-document py-5">
    <div class="container">
      <article>
        <h1>Refund &amp; Cancellation Policy</h1>
        <p class="legal-meta"><strong>Varnarc Private Limited</strong><br />Last updated: 10 April 2026</p>

        <h2>1. General Policy</h2>
        <p>All transactions are processed through third-party providers (Cashfree, Kwik API, banks, BBPS network).</p>

        <h2>2. Recharge Transactions</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Successful recharges are <strong>non-refundable</strong>.</li>
          <li>If recharge fails but money is deducted:
            <ul>
              <li>Refund will be processed within <strong>5–7 business days</strong>.</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. BBPS Bill Payments</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Once bill payment is successful → <strong>no cancellation allowed</strong>.</li>
          <li>Failed transactions will be auto-refunded.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Duplicate Transactions</h2>
        <p>Duplicate payments will be refunded after verification.</p>

        <h2>5. Failed / Pending Transactions</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>If transaction status is pending:
            <ul>
              <li>Wait for up to 24 hours.</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li>If failed:
            <ul>
              <li>Refund initiated automatically.</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2>6. Refund Timeline</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Wallet / UPI: 1–3 days</li>
          <li>Bank/Card: 5–7 business days</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>7. Refund Mode</h2>
        <p>Refunds will be processed:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>To original payment method only</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>8. Disputes</h2>
        <p>Users must report disputes within <strong>7 days</strong> of transaction.</p>

        <h2>9. Exceptions</h2>
        <p>Refunds may be denied if:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Incorrect details entered by user</li>
          <li>Successful transaction confirmed by operator</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>10. Contact</h2>
        <p>Email: <a href="mailto:support@varnarc.com">support@varnarc.com</a><br />
          Phone: <a href="tel:+919739723973">9739723973</a></p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </main>

  <%- include("../components/landing/footer") %>
  <%- include("../components/landing/scripts") %>
</body>

</html>
